Entries.Rainy_Day_1: Hey. I was just thinking about my old room in the basement. I felt comfortable there, but this is a lot more interesting. And I don't miss the smell...#$e#I felt kind of embarrassed living in my mum's house for so long.
Entries.Outdoor_4: We should raise more slimes... In big quantities they can be pretty profitable. And they're so easy to raise.#$e#Also, different coloured slimes produce different items. I dunno, I think it'd be kind of a fun hobby for us.
Entries.Neutral_6: If you need to go see your friends in town, go ahead. I like being alone, anyway.
Entries.fall_1: It seems like the whole valley's changed overnight... I guess autumn's finally here.
